## Fast gate (run after every task)

**Concurrent agents (default ‚Äî use this):**
```bash
# L0 gate ‚Äî ~15‚Äì45s
pnpm gate -- <path1> [path2 ...]
```

**Solo agent ‚Äî same L0 unless design-token / globals.css sweep:**
```bash
pnpm gate -- <path1> [path2 ...]
# or: pnpm lint:full  only when design-contract must re-run
```

**Before push:** use **batch-fix** (`.cursor/rules/gate-batch-fix-workflow.mdc`) ‚Äî one `pnpm gate:push`, fix all failures by category, one final `pnpm gate:push`. Do not L2 after every single fix.

```bash
pnpm gate:push
```

Both forms must exit 0. No exceptions. This is the non-negotiable close condition.
Full decision table: `.cursor/rules/targeted-verification.mdc`.

---

## Pre-push gate (run before opening a PR ‚Äî ~3 min)

```bash
pnpm verify:parallel
```

This includes knip, format check, all typechecks, and behavior tests. Run it once before pushing, not after every file edit.

